public abstract class AJsonObjectTokenProcessor extends Object
Abstract visitor JSON object token read processor for use with the GSON library. Assumes that the JSON reader is about to read an object. Provides default behavior for all the cases. Implementations should override the desired cases, saving values via their closures. Usage: To process the object token, run the process() method.
